Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.25,0:00:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,U.A. High School's hero course.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:04.45,0:00:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A training school for those whose goal is to acquire\Nthe necessary qualifications needed for pro heroes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.45,0:00:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Among similar courses across the country,\Ntheirs is the most popular and most competitive...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...and their acceptance rate is less\Nthan one in three hundred every year.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.35,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero who refused a National Honor Award—
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.05,0:00:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The number one hero, All Might.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero who resolved the most incidents in history—
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.55,0:00:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fiery Hero, Endeavor.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner of the Best Jeanist award eight years in a row—
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.45,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Best Jeanist.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:36.95,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Graduating from U.A. is a requirement\Nfor becoming a great hero.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.45,0:00:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I also tackled the U.A. entrance exam.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.70,0:00:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.45,0:00:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...the first step toward my dream of becoming a hero!
Comment: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:28.40,0:02:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a city!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They have more than one of these on the school grounds?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,U.A.'s amazing!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.40,0:02:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As it says in the application requirements,
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.10,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you listeners will be conducting\Nten-minute mock urban battles after this!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.95,0:02:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Three different types of faux villains\Nare stationed in each battle center.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.70,0:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You earn points for each of them\Nbased on their level of difficulty.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.85,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your goal, dear listeners, is to use your Quirks\Nto earn points by immobilizing the faux villains.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.60,0:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,680)}Mock battles...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,680)}How can everyone be so confident?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,680)}Aren't they nervous?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They even have equipment to go with their Quirks...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the person I met at the school gates!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:16.90,0:03:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The nice person!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She was assigned to the same battle center, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.70,0:03:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I have to thank her for earlier.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here, too?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl appears to be trying to focus.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.45,0:03:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you taking the entrance exam\Nto interfere with everyone else?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,680)}N-N-No, of course not...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.70,0:03:41.30,Alt,,0,0,0,,That guy's the one who was about to\Ntrip in front of the school gates, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.55,Alt,,0,0,0,,The one who winced after being called out.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.55,0:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, we have one\Nless rival to worry about, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky for us.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like the others think they\Nlucked out because I'm here...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, start!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:55.55,0:03:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no countdowns in real fights!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, run!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The die has been cast, you know!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.85,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huuuuh?!{What?!}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm behind already!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm behind.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, calm down.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's fine!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have All Might with me.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You swallowed the hair, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel any different, though...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think the stomach does?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.35,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll feel something in two or three hours.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:47.40,0:04:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to hurry back, take a shower, and eat breakfast.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.25,0:04:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have become a proper vessel,\Nbut it was one that was made in a hurry.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even get to take it for a test drive...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself for the physical\Nrepercussions it'll have on your body.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.75,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to explain\Nin detail, so I'll just tell you this.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.90,0:05:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When you use my Quirk, One For All, squeeze\Nyour buttocks and yell this inside your heart—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"S—"
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.80,0:05:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One point!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Target acquired.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.15,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming! It's coming!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I move?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, why?!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for distracting it!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.35,0:05:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A laser?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Merci!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a good team.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.60,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I don't think we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Adieu!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't meet again...?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Six minutes and two seconds left!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Oh no!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.00,0:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Points...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I need points fast!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.80,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The nice person!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's twenty-eight points...!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Twenty-eight?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty-five points!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty-five?!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's thirty-two!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's mine! Don't take it!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's first-come, first-served!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of enemies is decreasing fast!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.75,0:06:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.90,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In this practical exam, the examinees have not been\Ninformed of the number of villains or their locations.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a limited amount of time in a vast area.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to draw the villains out from there.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.95,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Information gathering ability to understand\Nthe situation before anyone else.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobility that can be used in many different circumstances.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:14.20,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment to be able to stay calm in any situation.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And pure combat ability.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.65,0:07:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,These basic abilities needed to keep the peace\Nin the streets are turned into points in this test.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this year's group look promising?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.90,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't know for sure yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:33.85,0:07:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Their true test is still to come.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,An obstacle that will go crazy in narrow spaces.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I recommend that you listeners try to avoid it.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little too big?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,An overwhelming threat.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How people act after they have\Nseen this shows their true nature.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to run away!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get points as I run...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, shoot, shoot, I'm still at zero points!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Less than two minutes left!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Two minutes?!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.65,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be wasted.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything All Might gave me...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be wasted!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.30,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad luck if you fell, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.05,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There is absolutely no merit in taking on that faux villain.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But that creates the opportunity...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...for it to shine brightly...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...and rise to the surface.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeeze your buttocks...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.00,Alt,,0,0,0,,...and yell this inside your heart—
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...and yell this inside your heart—
Dialogue: 2,0:09:48.80,0:09:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Smash...!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It rises to the surface—
Dialogue: 2,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important qualification of a hero—
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.00,0:10:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirit of self-sacrifice!
Comment: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.10,0:10:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,710)}The conditions are the same as when I tried to save Kacchan.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.95,0:10:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's different.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This time—
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute left!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, this is All Might's power.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm able to jump this high now.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.15,0:10:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Landing should be a piece of cake-cake-cake-cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Break"?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.55,0:11:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have become a proper vessel,\Nbut it was one that was made in a hurry.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself tor the physical\Nrepercussions it'll have on your body.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such an idiot!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.25,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A mere ten months was just barely enough time.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.95,0:11:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just barely hold this borrowed power.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was being conceited for a second!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:26.80,0:11:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been given the right to stand at the start line!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Think!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do? What to do?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Detroit Smash!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I aim that move at the ground...!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Both my legs and my right arm are broken.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have my left arm!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the timing—
Dialogue: 2,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm too early or too late, I'll die!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I succeed, I still won't have any points!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.10,0:12:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I break my left arm, there's no way I'll pass!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Release...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:30.95,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm safe...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she saved me...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she all right?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks uninjured, at least...?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.10,0:12:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...thank you!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:50.15,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can just get one point...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...up!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}was{\i0} that guy?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He suddenly jumped at the obstacle.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed to have a reinforcement-type Quirk...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...but that was unusual...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.55,0:13:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he had such an amazing Quirk, what kind\Nof life did he live that made him so jumpy?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was acting to trick others?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.30,0:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't look like he gained anything from doing so.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.15,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, there's no mistaking that he's an amazing guy.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're missing the point.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't they see?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He jumped out to save that girl.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.00,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was aware of the remaining time, his own\Nsafety, and the points he needed to pass...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And even so, he did not hesitate at all!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had not been in an exam...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...of course, I would have done the same!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Exam"...?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Of course"...?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:29.90,0:14:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good work.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, good work.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Here are some gummies.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat some gummies.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:41.95,0:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, you, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That mademoiselle...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...is the backbone of U.A.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.05,0:14:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...you were hurt this much by your own Quirk?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.90,0:15:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if his body is not used to his Quirk yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooooooch...!{Kiss...!}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,U.A. High's licensed school nurse...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.35,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Youthful Heroine, Recovery Girl!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Quirk is the super-activation of healing ability.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:26.25,0:15:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,U A. can only go through with such\Na reckless entrance exam because of her.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this quickly.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone else injured?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:38.85,0:15:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.70,0:15:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If this exam is set up like {\i1}that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he's...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Izuku...?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Izuku?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Izuku?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you smiling at the fish?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.70,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,From self-scoring, I know that I just\Nbarely passed the written exam.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.05,0:16:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was cancelled out by the\Nbig fat zero in the practical exam.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.35,0:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And ever since the entrance exam,\NI hadn't been able to contact All Might.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:39.40,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The results should arrive today or tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.55,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I think it's amazing that you even applied to U.A.!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even tell my mother about\Nwhat had happened with All Might.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:58.30,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept that secret so he could\Ncontinue being the Symbol of Peace.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no way I could tell anyone, not even my family.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All Might!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.85,0:17:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After you saw potential in me,\NI'm sorry I didn't live up to it!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did what I thought was right.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All Might, you...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Izu-lzu-lzu...!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Izu-lzu-lzu...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I-Izuku!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.95,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:35.95,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It came!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.75,0:18:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here as a projection!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.75,0:18:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All Might?!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, this is from U.A., right...?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:09.80,0:18:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:11.40,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to do some paperwork that took\Nsome time, so I couldn't contact you.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.65,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I came to this town to work at U.A.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All Might is working at U.A.?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.05,0:18:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrap it up?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.35,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is something I must talk to him about...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to push everything else back?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.65,0:18:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.65,0:18:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you passed the written exam,\Nyou got zero points on the practical exam.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that means you didn't pass—
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.50,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's so frustrating...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,—if that was all there was to it.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.70,0:19:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an entertainer, as well!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First, take a look at this video!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:19.00,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... um...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The nice person?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.70,0:19:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to negotiate directly in person after the exam!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.55,0:19:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Negotiate what?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep watching to find out!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.55,0:19:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... the person with curly hair...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...and freckles...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who I'm talking about?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... kind of plain-looking...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.80,0:19:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible for me to give him some of my points?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.80,0:19:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard him say, "If I can just get one point," so I thought...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.90,0:19:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...maybe he was still at zero points...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:59.45,0:20:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell can {\i1}you{\i0} do?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At least the points he lost because of me...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.55,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There was absolutely no reason\Nfor you to put yourself in danger!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He saved me!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:13.25,0:20:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please! Please!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:19.65,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to now having a Quirk,\Nyour actions spurred others to act.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:28.75,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The entrance exam the other day\Nwas not graded only on villain points!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you ask to, you cannot give him your points.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, there's no reason to give him any, female listener!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:44.90,0:20:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How can a hero course reject people\Nwho save others and do the right thing?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:51.45,0:20:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Perish the thought!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Call that lip service?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:55.85,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me!{Bring it on!}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:57.25,0:21:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a job that requires risking one's\Nlife to put that lip service into practice!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rescue points!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're given by a panel of judges.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.70,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the other basic ability we at U.A. look at!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:12.90,0:21:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Midoriya Izuku, sixty points!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.05,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And Uraraka Ochako, forty-five points!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You both pass.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too crazy...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, young Midoriya.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.75,0:21:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.10,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...your hero academia!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.45,0:21:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.25,0:21:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After receiving a lot of help...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...my life changed and will continue to change.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:58.40,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.05,0:22:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...my dream high school life is about to begin!
